data.name: Classic Margarita

ingredients.name: orange liqueur (like cointreau or triple sec)

data.quickTastyDescription: A refreshing classic cocktail made with just three simple ingredients: tequila, lime juice, and orange liqueur.
detailedCookingInstructions: Start by preparing your glass. Run a lime wedge around the rim of the glass and dip it into salt to coat the rim.
In a shaker, combine the tequila, lime juice, and orange liqueur with ice.
Strain the mixture into the prepared glass with or without ice, depending on your preference.
Garnish with a lime wedge on the rim. Enjoy!
